Bongiovi:





Raising his mighty axe, the grenade exploded against it, protecting Bongiovi 
from the explosion and most of the shrapnel.  He hissed, taking a quick 
glance at his axe noting it was still intact.  He spat a large glob of acid 
down at Khonkolor's back.
